黒川(くろかわ)あかねの今後が決まる</font>

243
00:15:31,138 --> 00:15:32,723
<font color="japanese">ハァ…</font>

244
00:15:32,806 --> 00:15:35,643
<font color="japanese">それなのに
こんな旅行に付いてきて</font>

245
00:15:35,726 --> 00:15:38,270
<font color="japanese">いつまでも恋リア気分で
いいのかしら？</font>

246
00:15:40,064 --> 00:15:42,024
<font color="japanese">もう恋リアじゃないもん</font>

247
00:15:42,650 --> 00:15:43,651
<font color="japanese">え…</font>

248
00:15:44,735 --> 00:15:46,111
<font color="japanese">あっ</font>

249
00:15:46,195 --> 00:15:48,614
<font color="japanese">ほ… 本当に
のぼせちゃったみたい</font>

250
00:15:48,697 --> 00:15:50,532
<font color="japanese">先に上がるね</font>

251
00:15:54,745 --> 00:15:57,289
<font color="japanese">（戸の開閉音）</font>

252
00:16:00,793 --> 00:16:03,003
<font color="japanese">まさかね</font>

253
00:16:15,683 --> 00:16:17,059
<font color="japanese">ハァ…</font>

254
00:16:19,979 --> 00:16:21,397
<font color="japanese">（ルビー）ねえ あかねちゃん</font>

255
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:22,314
<font color="japanese">ん…</font>

256
