<font color="japanese">そっか</font>

272
00:17:29,923 --> 00:17:32,384
<font color="japanese">もう遅いし そろそろ寝よう</font>

273
00:17:34,219 --> 00:17:36,388
<font color="japanese">うん そうだね</font>

